      • createGroup

        public void createGroup()
        Create a Wifi Direct group

        Will receive a Event.GROUP_CREATED if the group is created. If there is an error creating group Event.ERROR will be sent. If group already exists, no event will be sent. However, a Event.CONNECTED_AS_GROUP_OWNER should be received.
